              <path d="M11.192 15.757c0-.907-.188-1.754-.565-2.54a5.72 5.72 0 0 0-1.501-2.011 5.661 5.661 0 0 0-2.027-1.216 6.006 6.006 0 0 0-2.316-.432h-.8V7.558h.8c1.326 0 2.457-.482 3.39-1.447.933-.965 1.4-2.122 1.4-3.47h2.011c0 1.9-.663 3.51-1.99 4.83a6.837 6.837 0 0 1-4.83 1.99v.8c0 1.186.417 2.193 1.252 3.022.835.83 1.84 1.245 3.018 1.245h2.013v1.221zM22.013 15.757c0-.907-.188-1.754-.565-2.54a5.72 5.72 0 0 0-1.501-2.011 5.661 5.661 0 0 0-2.027-1.216 6.006 6.006 0 0 0-2.316-.432h-.8V7.558h.8c1.326 0 2.457-.482 3.39-1.447.933-.965 1.4-2.122 1.4-3.47H22.02c0 1.9-.663 3.51-1.99 4.83a6.837 6.837 0 0 1-4.83 1.99v.8c0 1.186.417 2.193 1.252 3.022.835.83 1.84 1.245 3.018 1.245h2.013v1.221z"/>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </div>
        <h4>Compra 100% Recomendada</h4>
        <p>"Aproveché la oferta de Compra 2 para regalarle uno a mi novio. Llegaron súper rápido a Cali en solo 5 días. Excelente atención y empaque premium."</p>
        <div class="testimonial-footer">— Sebastian R.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
